	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Puh! <delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ich dachte, <delay8 />du gehst irgendwo
